Description: Python no-IO library for the matrix chat protocol Nio is a multilayered Matrix client library. The underlying base layer doesn't do any IO on its own. On top of the base layer, a no-IO HTTP client implementation exists, as well as a full fledged batteries included asyncio layer using aiohttp. . Matrix is an open standard and lightweight protocol for real-time communication.
